The paper deals with image manipulation and specifically focuses on controlling the saliency of objects in images. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also uses optimization techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves patch-based manipulation, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM).
